{
  "video_id": "A_u2WFTfbcg",
  "title": "Where joy hides and how to find it | Ingrid Fetell Lee",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12786.0,
      "end_time": 14546.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s 2008,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 14571.0,
      "end_time": 18700.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m just finishing my first year of design school."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19740.0,
      "end_time": 21931.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m at my first year-end review,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21955.0,
      "end_time": 28822.0,
      "text": "which is a form of ritual torture for design students,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 28846.0,
      "end_time": 32569.0,
      "text": "where they make you take everything you made over the course of the year"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 32593.000000000004,
      "end_time": 34933.0,
      "text": "and lay it out on a table"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 34957.0,
      "end_time": 37818.0,
      "text": "and stand next to it while a bunch of professors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 37842.0,
      "end_time": 40563.0,
      "text": "most of whom you&#39;ve never seen before,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 40587.0,
      "end_time": 43206.0,
      "text": "give you their unfiltered opinions of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 44699.0,
      "end_time": 47890.0,
      "text": "So it&#39;s my turn and I&#39;m standing next to my table,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 47914.0,
      "end_time": 50710.0,
      "text": "everything neatly lined up,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 50734.0,
      "end_time": 54534.0,
      "text": "and I&#39;m just hoping that my professors can see"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 54558.0,
      "end_time": 60131.0,
      "text": "how much effort I&#39;ve put into making my designs practical"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 60155.0,
      "end_time": 63810.0,
      "text": "and ergonomic and sustainable."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 65430.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67290.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;m starting to get really nervous,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 67314.0,
      "end_time": 70604.0,
      "text": "because for a long time, no one says anything."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 70629.0,
      "end_time": 72580.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s just completely silent."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 73670.0,
      "end_time": 75946.0,
      "text": "And then one of the professors starts to speak, and he says,"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 75971.0,
      "end_time": 78448.0,
      "text": "\"Your work gives me a feeling of joy.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 79407.0,
      "end_time": 80557.0,
      "text": "Joy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 81467.0,
      "end_time": 84850.0,
      "text": "I wanted to be a designer because I wanted to solve real problems."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 84874.0,
      "end_time": 89232.0,
      "text": "Joy is nice, I guess, but it&#39;s kind of light --"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 89256.0,
      "end_time": 90695.0,
      "text": "not substantial."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 91921.0,
      "end_time": 93493.0,
      "text": "But I was also kind of intrigued,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 93517.0,
      "end_time": 98300.0,
      "text": "because joy is this intangible feeling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 98280.0,
      "end_time": 101579.0,
      "text": "and how does that come from the stuff on the table next to me?"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 102468.0,
      "end_time": 103686.0,
      "text": "I asked the professors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 103710.0,
      "end_time": 106119.0,
      "text": "\"How do things make us feel joy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 106143.0,
      "end_time": 111106.0,
      "text": "How do tangible things make us feel intangible joy?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 112306.0,
      "end_time": 116490.0,
      "text": "They hemmed and hawed and gestured a lot with their hands."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 117300.0,
      "end_time": 118782.0,
      "text": "\"They just do,\" they said."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 119907.0,
      "end_time": 121735.0,
      "text": "I packed up my things for the summer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 121759.0,
      "end_time": 124911.0,
      "text": "but I couldn&#39;t stop thinking about this question ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 126107.0,
      "end_time": 127576.0,
      "text": "and this launched a journey --"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 127600.0,
      "end_time": 130732.0,
      "text": "one that I didn&#39;t know at the time would take me 10 years --"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 130756.0,
      "end_time": 134219.0,
      "text": "to understand the relationship between the physical world"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 134243.0,
      "end_time": 139222.0,
      "text": "and the mysterious, quixotic emotion we call \"joy.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 140700.0,
      "end_time": 144137.0,
      "text": "And what I discovered is that not only are they linked,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 144161.0,
      "end_time": 147795.0,
      "text": "but that the physical world can be a powerful resource to us"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 147819.0,
      "end_time": 151423.0,
      "text": "in creating happier, healthier lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 152362.0,
      "end_time": 153541.0,
      "text": "After my review,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 153565.0,
      "end_time": 156380.0,
      "text": "I thought, \"I know what joy feels like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 156620.0,
      "end_time": 158371.0,
      "text": "but what is it, exactly?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 158717.0,
      "end_time": 162144.0,
      "text": "And I found that even scientists don&#39;t always agree,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 162168.0,
      "end_time": 165643.0,
      "text": "and they sometimes use the words \"joy\" and \"happiness\" and \"positivity\""
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 165667.0,
      "end_time": 167461.0,
      "text": "more or less interchangeably."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 168989.0,
      "end_time": 171878.0,
      "text": "But broadly speaking, when psychologists use the word joy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 171902.0,
      "end_time": 175307.0,
      "text": "what they mean is an intense, momentary experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 175331.0,
      "end_time": 176774.0,
      "text": "of positive emotion --"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 176798.0,
      "end_time": 180795.0,
      "text": "one that makes us smile and laugh and feel like we want to jump up and down."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 181152.0,
      "end_time": 183110.0,
      "text": "And this is actually a technical thing."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 183350.0,
      "end_time": 185360.0,
      "text": "That feeling of wanting to jump up and down"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 185600.0,
      "end_time": 188321.0,
      "text": "is one of the ways that scientists measure joy."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 189387.0,
      "end_time": 191500.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s different than happiness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 191290.0,
      "end_time": 193664.0,
      "text": "which measures how good we feel over time."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 193688.0,
      "end_time": 196672.0,
      "text": "Joy is about feeling good in the moment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 196696.0,
      "end_time": 197846.0,
      "text": "right now."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 199700.0,
      "end_time": 200481.0,
      "text": "And this was interesting to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 200505.0,
      "end_time": 204230.0,
      "text": "because as a culture, we are obsessed with the pursuit of happiness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 204470.0,
      "end_time": 207907.0,
      "text": "and yet in the process, we kind of overlook joy."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 210737.0,
      "end_time": 213904.0,
      "text": "So this got me thinking:"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 213928.0,
      "end_time": 215866.0,
      "text": "Where does joy come from?"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 216797.0,
      "end_time": 218370.0,
      "text": "I started asking everyone I knew,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 218394.0,
      "end_time": 221335.0,
      "text": "and even people I just met on the street,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 221359.0,
      "end_time": 223219.0,
      "text": "about the things that brought them joy."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 223243.0,
      "end_time": 226156.0,
      "text": "On the subway, in a café, on an airplane,"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 226180.0,
      "end_time": 229425.0,
      "text": "it was, \"Hi, nice to meet you. What brings you joy?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 230544.0,
      "end_time": 232320.0,
      "text": "I felt like a detective."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 232867.0,
      "end_time": 234792.0,
      "text": "I was like, \"When did you last see it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 234816.0,
      "end_time": 236603.0,
      "text": "Who were you with? What color was it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 236627.0,
      "end_time": 237802.0,
      "text": "Did anyone else see it?\""
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 238353.0,
      "end_time": 240607.0,
      "text": "I was the Nancy Drew of joy."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 240631.0,
      "end_time": 241781.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 242579.0,
      "end_time": 245960.0,
      "text": "And after a few months of this, I noticed that there were certain things"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 245984.0,
      "end_time": 249370.0,
      "text": "that started to come up again and again and again."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 249610.0,
      "end_time": 252344.0,
      "text": "They were things like cherry blossoms"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 252368.0,
      "end_time": 253672.0,
      "text": "and bubbles ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 254810.0,
      "end_time": 257929.0,
      "text": "swimming pools and tree houses ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 259728.0,
      "end_time": 263446.0,
      "text": "hot air balloons and googly eyes --"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 263470.0,
      "end_time": 264549.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 264573.0,
      "end_time": 267678.0,
      "text": "and ice cream cones, especially the ones with the sprinkles."
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 269172.0,
      "end_time": 274370.0,
      "text": "These things seemed to cut across lines of age and gender and ethnicity."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 274543.0,
      "end_time": 276200.0,
      "text": "I mean, if you think about it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 276440.0,
      "end_time": 278300.0,
      "text": "we all stop and turn our heads to the sky"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 278280.0,
      "end_time": 280831.0,
      "text": "when the multicolored arc of a rainbow streaks across it."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 281909.0,
      "end_time": 283448.0,
      "text": "And fireworks --"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 283472.0,
      "end_time": 285560.0,
      "text": "we don&#39;t even need to know what they&#39;re for,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 285584.0,
      "end_time": 288451.0,
      "text": "and we feel like we&#39;re celebrating, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 290860.0,
      "end_time": 293608.0,
      "text": "These things aren&#39;t joyful for just a few people;"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 293632.0,
      "end_time": 296461.0,
      "text": "they&#39;re joyful for nearly everyone."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 296485.0,
      "end_time": 298546.0,
      "text": "They&#39;re universally joyful."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 300504.0,
      "end_time": 302883.0,
      "text": "And seeing them all together,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 302907.0,
      "end_time": 306587.0,
      "text": "it gave me this indescribably hopeful feeling."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 308120.0,
      "end_time": 311101.0,
      "text": "The sharply divided, politically polarized world we live in"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 311125.0,
      "end_time": 316155.0,
      "text": "sometimes has the effect of making our differences feel so vast"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 316179.0,
      "end_time": 318800.0,
      "text": "as to be insurmountable."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 318104.0,
      "end_time": 319395.0,
      "text": "And yet underneath it all,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 319420.0,
      "end_time": 323520.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s a part of each of us that finds joy in the same things."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 324156.0,
      "end_time": 328283.0,
      "text": "And though we&#39;re often told that these are just passing pleasures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 328307.0,
      "end_time": 330861.0,
      "text": "in fact, they&#39;re really important,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 330885.0,
      "end_time": 334337.0,
      "text": "because they remind us of the shared humanity we find"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 334361.0,
      "end_time": 337173.0,
      "text": "in our common experience of the physical world."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 338309.0,
      "end_time": 339754.0,
      "text": "But I still needed to know:"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 339778.0,
      "end_time": 344433.0,
      "text": "What is it about these things that makes them so joyful?"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 345299.0,
      "end_time": 348207.0,
      "text": "I had pictures of them up on my studio wall,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 348231.0,
      "end_time": 351548.0,
      "text": "and every day, I would come in and try to make sense of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 352662.0,
      "end_time": 355294.0,
      "text": "And then one day, something just clicked."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 356144.0,
      "end_time": 358302.0,
      "text": "I saw all these patterns:"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 359422.0,
      "end_time": 360715.0,
      "text": "round things ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 361969.0,
      "end_time": 363905.0,
      "text": "pops of bright color ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 365512.0,
      "end_time": 367211.0,
      "text": "symmetrical shapes ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 368636.0,
      "end_time": 371433.0,
      "text": "a sense of abundance and multiplicity ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 372877.0,
      "end_time": 376261.0,
      "text": "a feeling of lightness or elevation."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 377328.0,
      "end_time": 378479.0,
      "text": "When I saw it this way,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 378503.0,
      "end_time": 382582.0,
      "text": "I realized that though the feeling of joy is mysterious and elusive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 382606.0,
      "end_time": 385924.0,
      "text": "we can access it through tangible, physical attributes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 385948.0,
      "end_time": 388762.0,
      "text": "or what designers call aesthetics,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 388786.0,
      "end_time": 392432.0,
      "text": "a word that comes from the same root as the Greek word \"aísthomai,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 392456.0,
      "end_time": 396452.0,
      "text": "which means, \"I feel,\" \"I sense,\" \"I perceive.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 397668.0,
      "end_time": 402119.0,
      "text": "And since these patterns were telling me that joy begins with the senses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 402143.0,
      "end_time": 404986.0,
      "text": "I began calling them \"Aesthetics of Joy\";"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 405100.0,
      "end_time": 406959.0,
      "text": "the sensations of joy."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 408484.0,
      "end_time": 410111.0,
      "text": "And in the wake of this discovery,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 410136.0,
      "end_time": 412281.0,
      "text": "I noticed something that as I walked around,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 412305.0,
      "end_time": 417396.0,
      "text": "I began spotting little moments of joy everywhere I went --"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 417420.0,
      "end_time": 418776.0,
      "text": "a vintage yellow car"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 418800.0,
      "end_time": 420722.0,
      "text": "or a clever piece of street art."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 420746.0,
      "end_time": 425479.0,
      "text": "It was like I had a pair of rose-colored glasses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 425503.0,
      "end_time": 428363.0,
      "text": "and now that I knew what to look for,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 428387.0,
      "end_time": 429741.0,
      "text": "I was seeing it everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 429765.0,
      "end_time": 433193.0,
      "text": "It was like these little moments of joy were hidden in plain sight."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 434870.0,
      "end_time": 436448.0,
      "text": "And at the same time,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 436472.0,
      "end_time": 437805.0,
      "text": "I had another realization,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 437829.0,
      "end_time": 440878.0,
      "text": "that if these are the things that bring us joy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 440902.0,
      "end_time": 443377.0,
      "text": "then why does so much of the world look like this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 443401.0,
      "end_time": 444990.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 445140.0,
      "end_time": 446545.0,
      "text": "Why do we go to work here?"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 447476.0,
      "end_time": 450165.0,
      "text": "Why do we send our kids to schools that look like this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 451384.0,
      "end_time": 453402.0,
      "text": "Why do our cities look like this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 454256.0,
      "end_time": 459660.0,
      "text": "And this is most acute for the places that house the people"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 459910.0,
      "end_time": 461219.0,
      "text": "that are most vulnerable among us:"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 461243.0,
      "end_time": 462576.0,
      "text": "nursing homes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 463312.0,
      "end_time": 464512.0,
      "text": "hospitals,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 465413.0,
      "end_time": 466806.0,
      "text": "homeless shelters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 467473.0,
      "end_time": 468848.0,
      "text": "housing projects."
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 469925.0,
      "end_time": 473139.0,
      "text": "How did we end up in a world that looks like this?"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 474992.0,
      "end_time": 477700.0,
      "text": "We all start out joyful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 477940.0,
      "end_time": 480668.0,
      "text": "but as we get older,"
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 480692.0,
      "end_time": 485205.0,
      "text": "being colorful or exuberant opens us up to judgment."
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 485883.0,
      "end_time": 491580.0,
      "text": "Adults who exhibit genuine joy are often dismissed as childish"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 491820.0,
      "end_time": 493142.0,
      "text": "or too feminine"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 493166.0,
      "end_time": 495328.0,
      "text": "or unserious"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 495352.0,
      "end_time": 497316.0,
      "text": "or self-indulgent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 498139.0,
      "end_time": 501734.0,
      "text": "and so we hold ourselves back from joy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 501758.0,
      "end_time": 504341.0,
      "text": "and we end up in a world that looks like this."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 505936.0,
      "end_time": 507842.0,
      "text": "But if the aesthetics of joy can be used"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 507866.0,
      "end_time": 510128.0,
      "text": "to help us find more joy in the world around us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 510152.0,
      "end_time": 512837.0,
      "text": "then couldn&#39;t they also be used to create more joy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 513537.00000000006,
      "end_time": 515971.00000000006,
      "text": "I spent that last two years scouring the planet,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 515995.0,
      "end_time": 519953.0,
      "text": "looking for different ways that people have answered this question."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 520719.00000000006,
      "end_time": 523232.00000000006,
      "text": "And this led me to the work of the artist Arakawa"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 523256.0,
      "end_time": 524987.0,
      "text": "and the poet Madeline Gins,"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 525110.0,
      "end_time": 529803.0,
      "text": "who believed that these kinds of environments are literally killing us."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 530686.0,
      "end_time": 534519.0,
      "text": "And so they set out the create an apartment building"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 534543.0,
      "end_time": 537580.0,
      "text": "that they believed would reverse aging."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 538313.0,
      "end_time": 539483.0,
      "text": "And this is it."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 540260.0,
      "end_time": 543241.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 543265.0,
      "end_time": 546758.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 546782.0,
      "end_time": 549751.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s a real place, just outside Tokyo."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 549775.0,
      "end_time": 553401.0,
      "text": "I spent a night there, and it&#39;s a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 553426.0,
      "end_time": 556125.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 556149.0,
      "end_time": 557886.0,
      "text": "The floors undulate,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 557910.0,
      "end_time": 560175.0,
      "text": "so you don&#39;t end up walking around"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 560199.0,
      "end_time": 562700.0,
      "text": "so much as kind of bouncing around the apartment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 562725.0,
      "end_time": 566957.0,
      "text": "and there are bright colors in every direction."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 568265.0,
      "end_time": 570602.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m not sure I left any younger,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 570626.0,
      "end_time": 574829.0,
      "text": "but it&#39;s as if, by trying to create an apartment"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 574854.0,
      "end_time": 576926.0,
      "text": "that would make us feel youthful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 576950.0,
      "end_time": 580280.0,
      "text": "they ended up creating one that was joyful."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 581277.0,
      "end_time": 583809.0,
      "text": "And yes, this is a bit much for everyday life,"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 583833.0,
      "end_time": 587238.0,
      "text": "but it made me wonder: What about the rest of us?"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 587263.0,
      "end_time": 591674.0,
      "text": "How do we bring these ideas back into the real world?"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 592621.0,
      "end_time": 595309.0,
      "text": "So I started finding people who were doing just that."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 595939.0,
      "end_time": 599943.0,
      "text": "For example, this hospital, designed by the Danish artist Poul Gernes."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 600674.0,
      "end_time": 602154.0,
      "text": "Or these schools,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 602178.0,
      "end_time": 604626.0,
      "text": "transformed by the non-profit Publicolor."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 605195.0,
      "end_time": 608734.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s interesting is that Publicolor has heard from school administrators"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 608758.0,
      "end_time": 611888.0,
      "text": "who say that attendance improves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 611912.0,
      "end_time": 613788.0,
      "text": "graffiti disappears"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 613812.0,
      "end_time": 617553.0,
      "text": "and kids actually say they feel safer in these painted schools."
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 618900.0,
      "end_time": 621870.0,
      "text": "And this aligns with research conducted in four countries,"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 621111.0,
      "end_time": 624738.0,
      "text": "which shows that people working in more colorful offices"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 624762.0,
      "end_time": 626416.0,
      "text": "are actually more alert,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 626441.0,
      "end_time": 627698.0,
      "text": "more confident"
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 627722.0,
      "end_time": 630669.0,
      "text": "and friendlier than those working in drab spaces."
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 632620.0,
      "end_time": 634212.0,
      "text": "Why would this be the case?"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 634236.0,
      "end_time": 638227.0,
      "text": "Well, as I started to trace back our love of color,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 638251.0,
      "end_time": 642553.0,
      "text": "I found that some researchers see a connection to our evolution."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 643292.0,
      "end_time": 648563.0,
      "text": "Color, in a very primal way, is a sign of life, a sign of energy."
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 649630.0,
      "end_time": 651920.0,
      "text": "And the same is true of abundance."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 651116.0,
      "end_time": 654466.0,
      "text": "We evolved in a world where scarcity is dangerous,"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 654490.0,
      "end_time": 657175.0,
      "text": "and abundance meant survival."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 658910.0,
      "end_time": 661314.0,
      "text": "So, one confetto --"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 661338.0,
      "end_time": 663568.0,
      "text": "which happens to be the singular of confetti,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 663592.0,
      "end_time": 664989.0,
      "text": "in case you were wondering --"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 665130.0,
      "end_time": 666378.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 666402.0,
      "end_time": 668463.0,
      "text": "isn&#39;t very joyful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 668487.0,
      "end_time": 669910.0,
      "text": "but multiply it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 669934.0,
      "end_time": 672697.0,
      "text": "and you have a handful of one of the most joyful substances"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 672721.0,
      "end_time": 673871.0,
      "text": "on the planet."
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 674494.0,
      "end_time": 678479.0,
      "text": "The architect Emmanuelle Moureaux uses this idea in her work a lot."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 678503.0,
      "end_time": 680295.0,
      "text": "This is a nursing home she designed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 680319.0,
      "end_time": 684756.0,
      "text": "where she uses these multicolored spheres to create a feeling of abundance."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 685752.0,
      "end_time": 688160.0,
      "text": "And what about all those round things I noticed?"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 689159.0,
      "end_time": 692451.0,
      "text": "Well, it turns out neuroscientists have studied this, too."
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 692475.0,
      "end_time": 694896.0,
      "text": "They put people into fMRI machines,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 694920.0,
      "end_time": 699266.0,
      "text": "and they showed them pictures of angular objects and round ones."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 700110.0,
      "end_time": 702416.0,
      "text": "And what they found is that the amygdala,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 702441.0,
      "end_time": 706670.0,
      "text": "a part of the brain associated in part with fear and anxiety,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 706910.0,
      "end_time": 708280.0,
      "text": "lit up when people looked at angular objects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 708304.0,
      "end_time": 710304.0,
      "text": "but not when they looked at the round ones."
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 711310.0,
      "end_time": 714829.0,
      "text": "They speculate that because angles in nature"
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 714854.0,
      "end_time": 718387.0,
      "text": "are often associated with objects that might be dangerous to us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 718411.0,
      "end_time": 723425.0,
      "text": "that we evolved an unconscious sense of caution around these shapes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 723450.0,
      "end_time": 726450.0,
      "text": "whereas curves set us at ease."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 726637.0,
      "end_time": 730512.0,
      "text": "You can see this in action in the new Sandy Hook Elementary School."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 731257.0,
      "end_time": 733260.0,
      "text": "After the mass shooting there in 2012,"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 733284.0,
      "end_time": 735253.0,
      "text": "the architects Svigals + Partners"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 735277.0,
      "end_time": 738540.0,
      "text": "knew that they needed to create a building that was secure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 738564.0,
      "end_time": 740810.0,
      "text": "but they wanted to create one that was joyful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 740835.0,
      "end_time": 742528.0,
      "text": "and so they filled it with curves."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 742552.0,
      "end_time": 745393.0,
      "text": "There are waves running along the side of the building,"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 745417.0,
      "end_time": 748758.0,
      "text": "and these squiggly canopies over the entryway,"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 748782.0,
      "end_time": 751686.0,
      "text": "and the whole building bends toward the entrance"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 751710.0,
      "end_time": 753366.0,
      "text": "in a welcoming gesture."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 755726.0,
      "end_time": 758349.0,
      "text": "Each moment of joy is small,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 758373.0,
      "end_time": 762583.0,
      "text": "but over time, they add up to more than the sum of their parts."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 764553.0,
      "end_time": 767892.0,
      "text": "And so maybe instead of chasing after happiness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 767916.0,
      "end_time": 771940.0,
      "text": "what we should be doing is embracing joy"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 771118.0,
      "end_time": 776630.0,
      "text": "and finding ways to put ourselves in the path of it more often."
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 777697.0,
      "end_time": 778886.0,
      "text": "Deep within us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 778910.0,
      "end_time": 783808.0,
      "text": "we all have this impulse to seek out joy in our surroundings."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 784453.0,
      "end_time": 786552.0,
      "text": "And we have it for a reason."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 787223.0,
      "end_time": 790675.0,
      "text": "Joy isn&#39;t some superfluous extra."
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 791573.0,
      "end_time": 796693.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s directly connected to our fundamental instinct for survival."
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 797885.0,
      "end_time": 800129.0,
      "text": "On the most basic level,"
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 800153.0,
      "end_time": 804881.0,
      "text": "the drive toward joy is the drive toward life."
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 805534.0,
      "end_time": 806684.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 806708.0,
      "end_time": 808592.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 808616.0,
      "end_time": 809766.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 809791.0,
      "end_time": 810977.0,
      "text": "Thank you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 811100.0,
      "end_time": 812151.0,
      "text": "thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 812176.0,
      "end_time": 817603.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}